::Punch/Dark One/Pyro/Nemesis Enforcer::

Punch yells as his gun is shot out of his hands, quickly grabbing another 
one. Pyro sees the blast coming at him, lifting Tavatron to block it.

Punch growls. "Blast doors close, internal defences open fire! KILL HIM!"

Two blast doors close on either side of the bots, trapping Tygerhawk with 
them. Autoguns pop out from the cealing and walls, opening fire at the 
suicidal fuzor. Punch also opens fire.

Dark One and Pyro back away, Dark One slamming his rifle once again at Iron 
Raptor's head.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
"Warning, weapon fire detected inside base."

Nemesis Enforcer jumps up as the computer reports this, checking the scanners 
for the location of weapon fire, running off to there with his gun ready.
